**Example - passing previous agent output to the next agent using `variables`:**

First execution block (agent A produces data):
```python
customer_list = await delegate_to_crm_agent("Get all customers with id and email")
print(customer_list)
```
After execution you get variables e.g. `customer_list` in the Variables Summary.

Second execution block (pass that variable to agent B):
```python
report = await delegate_to_analytics_agent("Summarize these customers and suggest top 5", variables=["customer_list"])
print(report)
```
Here `variables=["customer_list"]` passes the output from the first agent into the second agent.

